                        <li><i class='bx bx-check'></i> No sign-up required</li>
                        <li><i class='bx bx-check'></i> Process images up to 50 megapixels[citation:1]</li>
                        <li><i class='bx bx-check'></i> Download as PNG with transparent background</li>
